docs.lead_paragraph: Opinions differ on whether young stars like Rory McIlroy, Bubba Watson and Jason Day can attract viewers in large numbers when Woods’s playing days are over.
docs.abstract: Opinions differ on prospects for the PGA Tour now that Tiger Woods' career appears to be permanently on the wane; some feel that rising talents like Rory McIlroy will successfully fill void, while other say no current players have star power necessary to invigorate and reforge the game as Woods did.

headline.main: As Tiger Woods Fades, a Fear That Revenue Will, Too
